<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Simply Rénovation — Portail Sécurisé</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #0e0f11;
      --surface: #16181c;
      --surface2: #1e2127;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      --border2: rgba(255,255,255,0.13);
      --text: #f0f0f0;
      --text-muted: #8a8f99;
      --accent: #4ade80;
      --radius: 16px;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .topbar {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 0 32px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      height: 64px;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }
    .brand {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .brand span { color: var(--accent); }
    .badge-ssl {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      background: rgba(74,222,128,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.2);
      padding: 5px 12px;
      border-radius: 100px;
    }

    .hero {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 60px auto 40px;
      padding: 0 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      background: var(--surface2);
      padding: 6px 16px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    h1 span { color: var(--accent); }

    .layout {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .step-dot {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      background: rgba(74,222,128,0.1);
      color: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-right: 12px;
    }

    .grid2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; }

    label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    input, select {
      background: var(--surface2);
      border: 1px solid var(--border2);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: inherit;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }

    .upload-zone {
      border: 2px dashed var(--border2);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .btn-submit {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #0e0f11;
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-top: 20px;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-submit:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); opacity: 0.9; }

    .bareme-card {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--surface), var(--bg));
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="topbar">
    <div class="brand">SIMPLY <span>RÉNOVATION</span></div>
    <div class="badge-ssl">🔒 SSL SÉCURISÉ</div>
  </nav>

  <header class="hero">
    <div class="hero-tag">Portail Client Accrédité</div>
    <h1>SOUMETTEZ VOTRE DOSSIER <span>DE RÉNOVATION</span></h1>
  </header>

  <main class="layout">
    <div class="main-content">
      <form action="https://formsubmit.co/sofianeb28@gmail.com" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        
        <div class="card">
          <h2 style="font-family:'Syne'; margin-bottom:24px;"><span class="step-dot">01</span>COORDONNÉES PRINCIPALES</h2>
          <div class="grid2">
            <div class="field">
              <label>Civilité</label>
              <select name="civilite"><option>Monsieur</option><option>Madame</option></select>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>Téléphone</label>
              <input type="tel" name="telephone" placeholder="06 12 34 56 78" required>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>Nom</label>
              <input type="text" name="nom" required>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>Prénom</label>
              <input type="text" name="prenom" required>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label>Adresse E-mail</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="votre@email.com" required>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2 style="font-family:'Syne'; margin-bottom:24px;"><span class="step-dot">02</span>PIÈCES JUSTIFICATIVES</h2>
          <div class="upload-zone">
            <input type="file" name="documents" multiple required>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 10px;">
              Déposez vos fichiers (Avis d'imposition, CNI, RIB...)
            </p>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">ENVOYER MON DOSSIER COMPLET</button>
        </div>

      </form>
    </div>

    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="bareme-card">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Syne'; font-size:0.9rem; margin-bottom:12px;">TABLEAU DES REVENUS 2025</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.75rem; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.5;">
          Les plafonds de l'ANAH varient selon votre zone géographique (Zone 1 ou Zone 2).
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top:15px; display:flex; gap:10px;">
          <div style="flex:1; background:var(--surface2); padding:10px; border-radius:8px; font-size:0.7rem; text-align:center;">ZONE 1</div>
          <div style="flex:1; background:var(--surface2); padding:10px; border-radius:8px; font-size:0.7rem; text-align:center;">ZONE 2</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </main>

</body>
</html>
